/09/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T134056.095.jpg?fit=1000%2C1000&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T134056.095.jpg?fit=1000%2C1000&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T134056.095.jpg?fit=1000%2C1000&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T134056.095.jpg?fit=1000%2C1000&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 13624, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/10/12/matr-bruce-springsteen-sting-billy-joel-elton-john-and-friends-jailhouse-rock/", "url_meta": {"origin": 235, "position": 1}, "title": "MatR: Bruce Springsteen, Sting, Billy Joel, Elton John, and Friends &#8211; Jailhouse Rock", "author": "Ken", "date": "October 12, 2019", "format": false, "excerpt": "At an Elvis-themed benefit concert, Bruce joined Sting, Billy Joel, Elton John, Paul Simon, and more great performers on an encore of Elvis' classic \"Jailhouse Rock.\"", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/jailhouse.jpg?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/jailhouse.jpg?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/jailhouse.jpg?fit=600%2C600&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 13047, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1987/03/04/matr-bruce-springsteen-and-bruce-hornsby-you-sexy-thing/", "url_meta": {"origin": 235, "position": 2}, "title": "You Sexy Thing", "author": "Ken", "date": "March 4, 1987", "format": false, "excerpt": "It doesn't